            {
              "external_url": "",
              "href": "/docs/api/ops/diagonal",
              "kind": "link",
              "target": "diagonal",
              "text": "we.diagonal"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " if you use this\nfunction to extract a diagonal and wish to write to the resulting array;\nwhether it returns a copy or a view depends on what version of numpy you\nare using."
